viewData.name: PhiBrows Goldenbrown SUPE Pigment 5ml - 2pcs
viewData.short_description: Golden brown is the lightest in the palette of PhiBrows mixed pigments. It is used with extremely light natural hair and eyebrows. It is mostly used in Scandinavian countries, Germany and Russia. It can also be used with grey hair, pure or in combination with one or two drops of Yellow pigment.
viewData.long_description: Golden brown is the lightest in the palette of PhiBrows mixed pigments. It is used with extremely light natural hair and eyebrows. It is mostly used in Scandinavian countries, Germany and Russia. It can also be used with grey hair, pure or in combination with one or two drops of Yellow pigment. contains 2 pieces of 5ml pigment
